title: Finding Your Place Of Blessing | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: Finding Your Place Of Blessing | Joel Osteen
description:
God has designed specific places for you to thrive. His blessings for your life are connected to the place He's called you to be. 

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
